<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Jan1933"><font color="red">4 January 1933</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Paul L&eacute;on): Mr Joyce &hellip; the situation has to a great extent exhausted him both physically and morally. He tries to react by working very hard, at least as much as he has the chance, but I have seen him suffering so deeply and with such disastrous effects on his strength that my impression is that he is sometimes at the end of his forces </div>
